title: Three Throws and a Little Brady
description:
Mina and ESPN's Field Yates discuss the Patriots-Bills game and whether or not there's anything that will carry over when they meet again in Week 16, the state of the Bucs, the Dolphins turnaround on defense and Tua's RPO effectiveness, the Cowboys-WFT matchup, and whether or not the Browns should pay Baker Mayfield.
